<script type="text/javascript">
	$(document).ready(function() {
        var searchtext = $('.jll-search-label').text();
        $('.jll-search-toggle,.jll-submit-search').attr('title', searchtext);
        $('.jll-search-form input').attr('placeholder', searchtext);


		$('.jll-search-toggle').click(function() {
			$('#jllnavbar').toggleClass('jll-navbar-mode-search');
			$('#jll-globalnav-search input').focus();
			return false;
		});


		$('.jll-cancel-search').click(function() {
			$('#jllnavbar').toggleClass('jll-navbar-mode-search');
			return false;
		});	

		$('.jll-navbar-toggle').click(function() {
			$('#jllnavbar').toggleClass('jll-navbar-expanded');
		});

		$('#jllnavbar h2').click(function(evt) {
			if (!$(evt.target).is('a')) {
				$(this).closest('div').toggleClass('submenu-expanded');
				return false;
			}
		});


		function JLLNavigateToSearch() {
		    var query = $('.jll-search-form input[type=text]').val();
		    if (query) {
		        var submitURL = $('.jll-search-form').data('submiturl');
		        document.location = submitURL + "?k=" + query;
		    }
		    return false;
		}

		$('.jll-submit-search').click(JLLNavigateToSearch);

		$('.jll-search-form input[type=text]').keypress(function (e) {
		    var key = e.which;
		    if (key == 13)  // the enter key code
		    {
		        JLLNavigateToSearch();
		        return false;
		    }
		});
	});
</script>
